		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's no suprise that some PD games show problems, as those were likely never actually tested on an NES (just in emulators).
<br />
<br />And I wonder if that Russian Pirate was tested on an NES either.  My money is it being tested on a famiclone (if even that).
<br />
<br />Of the ROMs mentioned -- the ones that HAVE been run on an NES with expected results are blargg's test ROMs -- which confirm his findings.
<br />
<br />
<br />But of course I can't say anything definitively, so I join you in waiting for someone to actually test said ROMs and report back.
<br />
<br />(Man I need a devcart)

		

